If you want to comment multiple lines,the steps blow you can process.


Select the multiple lines of code you want to comment.
Press Ctrl + K, then Ctrl + C (Windows) or Command + K, then Command + C (Mac).

Uncomment multiple lines of code:
Select the multiple lines of code you want to uncomment.
Press Ctrl + K, then Ctrl + U (Windows) or Command + K, then Command + U (Mac).

and the development environment is visual studio,I haven't tried the others yet.
